plot: Kara helps Hank face his painful past when a White Martian, who wiped out all of the Green Martians from Mars, kidnaps Senator Miranda Crane who is an anti-alien politician. Adam Foster who is Cat's estranged son arrives in National City.

A Senator who opposes alien presence on Earth comes to National City to speak. And it's while she's speaking that an alien appears and grabs her. That's when the DEO shows up and Hank is frozen when he sees the alien. He reveals the alien is the one that wiped out his people. They later find the alien's lair and rescue the Senator. They bring her to the DEO and she asks Hank about rumors of an alien at the DEO. Hank evades answering her. Later Kara learns the Senator is the alien. They try to get it but it gets away. Hank says it came to get him. Cat's son comes to see her because Kara sent the letter she wrote but decided not to send it.—rcs0411@yahoo.com
